sical theories where time is\nfundamentally discrete, characterizing the classical limit of discrete-time\nquantum dynamics, and proving complexity results for quantum circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2016 21:26:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Aug 2017 17:55:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-15"}
